summary: Descend into the darkness. Cleaned with TES5Edit
descriptionHtml:
[IMG]http://static.skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/images/13965-1-1355171980.png[/IMG]

[b][color=orange][size=4]Description[/size][/color][/b]
Welcome to Castle Brennenburgh, the famed location of Amnesia: The Dark Descent. This mod is currently on hold until I\'m done college for the year, and I finish all my current projects I\'m currently involved with. The location of the dungeon is west of Riverwood. You\'ll know when you\'re close.[/b]

[b][color=red][size=4]Installing[/size][/color][/b]
Copy the scripts folder and Castle Brennenburgh.esp into the Data Folder.


[b][color=orange][size=4]Mod Recommendations[/size][/color][/b] 
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=17416]Wearable Lanterns[/url]

[b][color=orange][size=4]NEWS[/size][/color][/b] 
[i]Cleaned with TES5Edit. Hopefully those with issues will no longer have problems.[/i]

[b][color=green][size=4]Permissions and Credit[/size][/color][/b]
[b]I am not allowing any redistribution of this file under any circumstance. Credit goes to Frictional Games for creating Amnesia: The Dark Descent[/b]
author: Daemon White
